On this occasion of the celebration of the most important factor of production, we at the Federal Airports Authority of Nigeria heartily felicitate with our labour force. According to the statement endorsed by Capt. Rabiu H. Yadudu, MD/CE of FAAN and sent to the AmehNews saying We make bold to say that your commitment, resilience, dedication, hard work and ingenuity are the key variables that are responsible for our successes and achievements over the years. Your invaluable contributions to the aviation industry and indeed Nigeria are highly commendable, even in the face of daunting challenges. As we celebrate your day, be rest assured that the Authority holds you in high esteem, and will continue to prioritise and support your growth, development, aspirations and well-being. Congratulations; Happy Workers Day. 